\backslash
_rate$
\end_layout

\end_inset

) is related to population growth, but it provides a more direct, concurrent
 measure for housing market pressures.
 More importantly, it captures the TABOR growth factor (new construction)
 in a straightforward way.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Vacancy
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

Rate
